
    This directory contains the information needed to make STSDAS run as
an external package within IRAF.  It also contains special libraries used 
within STSDAS.

Libraries in this directory:
	libapplib	applications subroutines (applib directory)
	libdisplay	terminal display subroutines (display directory)
	libf77util	F77VOS utiltity subroutines (f77util directory)
	libiraf77	F77VOS interface subroutines (iraf77 directory)
	libstieee	STSDAS special ieee file format subroutines (stieee dir)
	libstxtools	STSDAS special application tools (xtools directory)
	libsynphot	STSDAS synthetic photometry library (synphot directory)
	libtbtables	STSDAS table I/O subroutines (tbtables directory)
	libuttables	STSDAS table utilities (uttables directory)
	stalone		F77 stand-alone interface (stalone directory)

Other necessary files:
	helpdb.mip	host independent help database for STSDAS
	iraf77.inc	F77VOS interface include file
	mkpkg		mkpkg for this directory
	mkpkg.inc	special mkpkg instructions for STSDAS
	mkpkg.sf.*	operating system specific mkpkg instructions
	root.hd		root help directory for STSDAS
	rootstsdas.hd	root task entry for STSDAS help tree
	strip.stsdas	list of files to be deleted when run `mkpkg strip'
	zzsetenv.def	STSDAS environment variables used
	

